snippet: Shanshan Feng of China won the Dubai Ladies Masters by five strokes after shooting a three-under 69 to capture her second Ladies European Tour title.
abstract: Shanshan Feng wins the Dubai Ladies Masters golf tournament to capture her second Ladies European Tour title; other golf news noted.
